	(35,2,'2014-07-29 06:23:20','2014-07-29 06:23:20','Generous donations of time and money allow us to continue to provide a comfortable home-away-from-home for the families who need our services. There are many ways you can help, and your kindness is always appreciated.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Make a <a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"https://ronaldhouse-sf.ejoinme.org/MyPages/DonationPage/tabid/229897/Default.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">financial contribution</a>.</li>\r\n	<li>Donate stock or estate gifts.</li>\r\n	<li>Sponsor our annual Gala and/or Golf Tournament.</li>\r\n	<li>Volunteer your time.</li>\r\n	<li>Invite us to do a presentation about the Ronald McDonald House for your organization or club.</li>\r\n	<li>Contribute items from our <a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/how-you-can-help/wish-list/\">wishlist</a>.</li>\r\n	<li><a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"http://www.donatingiseasy.org/donate-car-any-charity.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Donate a vehicle</a>.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nOur Federal EIN is 94-2951627. For additional information, email us at <a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"mailto:info@ronaldhouse-sf.org\">info@ronaldhouse-sf.org</a>.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter\" title=\"Volulnteers Cleaning\" src=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/test/wp-content/uploads/2012/03/Volulnteers-Cleaning.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"824\" height=\"620\" />','Donate','','publish','open','open','','donate','','','2014-08-01 21:17:32','2014-08-01 21:17:32','',33,'http://rmh.dev?page_id=35',0,'page','',0),
