	(265,1,'2014-11-19 18:41:52','2014-11-19 18:41:52','<div id=\"body-wrapper\" style=\"color: #000000;\">\n<div id=\"body\">\n<div id=\"content-single\" class=\"content-single content-singular content-page\">\n<div id=\"post-1718\" class=\"post-1718 page type-page status-publish hentry\">\n<div class=\"content-single\">\n<div class=\"page-restrict-output\">\n\n&nbsp;\n\nRegistration is open for the 2014 Patrick Marleau Golf Classic on August 25th! Book your sponsorship today!\n\n<strong><a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"https://ronaldhouse-sf.ejoinme.org/?tabid=522209\">REGISTER ONLINE</a><a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"http://ronaldhouse-sf.org/\">\n</a></strong>\n\n<strong>THE 25TH ANNUAL GOLF CLASSIC BENEFITING </strong><strong>RONALD MCDONALD HOUSE OF SAN FRANCISCO</strong>\n\n<a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/logo_PMGC_2014_cropped2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1748\" src=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/logo_PMGC_2014_cropped2.jpg\" alt=\"logo_PMGC_2014_cropped2\" width=\"175\" height=\"232\" /></a>\n\nMonday, August 25, 2014\n\nRegistration 8:30am || Shotgun start at 10:30am\n\nLake Merced Golf Club\n2300 Junipero Serra Blvd.\nDaly City, CA 94015\n\nAct now – last year’s tournament was a sold-out event.\n\nThank you to our early sponsors!\n\n<a style=\"color: #780005;\" href=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/email-invite-publisher-presenting.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1921\" src=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/email-invite-publisher-presenting-1024x863.jpg\" alt=\"email invite publisher - presenting\" width=\"1024\" height=\"863\" /></a><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1914\" src=\"http://www.ronaldhouse-sf.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/email-invite-publisher-challenges-1024x571.jpg\" alt=\"email invite publisher - challenges\" width=\"1024\" height=\"571\" /><a 